title: Plimsouls
description:
The Plimsouls Discography
Ripped and Purchased myself in FLAC format, from original CD source.  Live At The Palomino Club, was created from 320k VBR mp3 format source.

Studio Albums:
The Plimsouls...Plus (bonus tracks)
Everywhere At Once
Kool Trash

Live Albums:
Live! Beg, Borrow & Steal (October 31, 1981 Whisky A Go Go)
Beach Town Confidential (Live at the Golden Bear 1983)
Live At The Palomino Club
One Night In America

I've included CD cover art in each folder.

All of these were ripped by me into FLAC from the original CDs, or purchased via iTunes.  Only Live At The Palomino Club is not in lossless, as my only source was 320k vbr MP3 files.

I hope you enjoy the torrent, and please comment!
